{
  "stem": "26142.10",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his daughter was one that I went to school with.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I had a friend-- we were a little bit more than friendly with his-- her name was Tova.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Next night-- we could barely wait till next night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Next night, we heard quietly that the door of that mikvah opened up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We couldn't see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was pitch-black dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This girl Tova came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she-- she brought us-- she brought us food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She brought us wurst and bread, and some sodas to drink.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she told us that Dudie-- that Neuman went and talked to our parents, that our father instructed us that we should stay there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He is going to travel the next day to the-- to a village, which was the county-- head of the county called [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Wolow. ?] He will-- he will-- and he will try to do something to-- to get us out of here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because we cannot stay in the Carpathian anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We have to get deep inside Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So-- and she asked us what-- if we need anything, what.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She will come tomorrow and bring it to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we told her the first thing we need is-- is a watch-- because we didn't have anymore-- so that we know the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, if possible, she should bring us cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Under the great-- we were both smokers at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Under the great tension, without-- without cigarettes it was--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and we have to wait till further instructions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we stayed on that attic [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] three days-- three days, four nights and three days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next day, my father managed to go to get to the city [?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
